description:
Dane Mitchellâ€™s Post hoc conjures up the ghosts of our past, calling up millions of vanished, extinct, absent  and obsolete things. From submerged atolls to failed utopias, extinct languages to tax havens, long lists of lost, withdrawn and vanished entities and phenomena are announced and transmitted, accumulating as a forecast of the past.  
You can find more info via posthoc.xyz
